relation: My favorite chapter in the game and it also sports my favorite boss in the game. Could it get any better? They will, they will shock you!!
fanart of a non-boss character in a short chapter.
The second Gameplay Point event of the Earthbound Fanfest of 2010. Unlike the last one, I didn't bother submitting this one.

This was a hard one to draw. Because I couldn't figure out where I wanted everyone to be, I actually had to start this one over a couple times before I was satisfied with the end result. So many bosses in that chapter.
Of the three games overall, this is my favorite zombie character. A zombie armadillo? Certainly didn't see this one coming.
